channel.title: RetaliationX- New Server, Good layout for eco, Good PvP & PvM
channel.description:
Hey I'm not the owner of this server but I am really enjoying it. At the moment we are really low on population because the server just opened up last week! Be some of the first people in on a great server and have first grabs! Has custom bosses, adjustable gameframes, fun mini games, fun pk, donator island all custom.
http://retaliationx.com/forum/forum.php that is the link to the forum and from there you can find the web client for easy access.
SEE YA THERE
